1 b. The superintenden t of public instruction shall compile and publish assessmen t
2 results in accordance with sections 15.1 - 21 - 09 and 15.1 - 21 - 10 .
3 c. The superintenden t of public instruction shall administer an annual parenta l
4 satisfaction survey requesting each parent of an eligible studen t receiving an
